2036131775.text: "However, parkin monoubiquitination of Bcl2 enhances the ability of Bcl2 to bind beclin 1 and suppress autophagy, and RNAi knockdown of parkin increases the LC3-II band in 293, SH-SY5Y, and primary neuron cultures [XREF_BIBR]."
